With the release on July 14, 2021, the Monthly Survey of Manufacturing (MSM) has published revised estimates. Estimates of sales of goods manufactured, inventories and orders have been revised back to January 2018.

On March 14, 2023, The Monthly Survey of Manufacturing uses North American Industry Classification System (NAICS) Canada 2022 Version 1.0 replacing North American Industry Classification System (NAICS) Canada 2017 Version 3.0.

As of May 16, 2023, the data has been updated to 2017 dollars (2017=100). For data based on 2012 dollars, please see the historical (real-time) table 16-10-0014-01 and historical releases up to April 2023.
